Is that because MethodHelper needs a mutable handle (why?)? Seems like unnecessary overhead.

3694:2-3694:44
Sun Aug 24 19:30:21 2014 +0000
Author: Ian Rogers <1010118@85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889>
Parent: 13f169a2_1a08bab9
UUID: 9399d985_f2bb48a6
